title: Joe Rogan Experience Review of Bob Lazar 2
description:
JRE Review of Bob Lazar....2

Why do another review of Bob Lazar?! Why the F-not?! Many of you reached out to me saying how interested they were in having Bob on Rogan's podcast and that this has opened their eyes to things or just spiked a huge interest. After requests to talk more about the guy and a Rogan/UFO fan wanting to come on (who got stuck in LA traffic..Sorry bud) I felt it was time to do another. Review 2.. Let's go!

Enjoy my review folks!

Follow me on Instagram at www.instagram.com/joeroganexperiencereview

Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6ilK4Zrqk2ZeowbOo7pXgw?

Please email me here with any suggestions and questions for future shows..
